dc_description_s: Accompanied by: Verzeichnisteil zum Falkplan Berlin. Includes 8 ancillary maps of "Innenstadtkarte Berlin (west) 1:7500," "Berlin 1:200000," "Frohnau, Waidmannslust, Lübars, & Hermsdorf 1:31500," "U-Bahn & S-Bahn," "Biesdorf, Köpenick, Kaulsdorf, & Mahlsdorf 1:31500," "Ausstellungsgelände Internationales Congress Centrum 1:10500," "Adlershot, Altglienicke, Köpenick, & Grünau 1:31500" and "Friedrichshagen, Müggelheim, Rahnsdorf, & Schmöckwitz 1:43500."
